	Source : &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.howtogeek.com/howto/windows-vista/create-a-shortcut-or-hotkey-for-the-safely-remove-hardware-dialog/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; title=&quot;Create a Shortcut or Hotkey for the Safely Remove Hardware Dialog&quot;&gt;Create a Shortcut or Hotkey for the Safely Remove Hardware Dialog&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h6&gt;
